<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/tips.css"></head><body><p><b>Build diff diagram</b></p><p>If your project is under version control, you can build a UML diagram that reflects your local changes and visualizes relationships between the modified components.</p><p>Press <span class="shortcut">&shortcut:UML.ShowChanges;</span> and select the necessary changelist to build the diagram. Double-click a node on the diagram to see the change in the diff dialog. </p><p class="image"><img src="images/ij_tips_showDiffOnDiagram.png" alt="Show Changes Diagram" style="border: 1px solid #55555;" /></p></body></html>